const SlotDetails = ({ slot }) => { return (

{slot.module}

Type: {slot.lessonType}

Class: {slot.classNo}

Day: {slot.day}

Start: {slot.startTime}

End: {slot.endTime}

Weeks: {slot.weeks}

Class: {slot.classNoWanted}

Start: {slot.startTimeWanted}
